cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.GR 

The paper deals with image denoising techniques and benchmarking them on real photographs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves statistical modeling and regression analysis, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper deals with image processing and post-processing, which could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves evaluating and comparing different denoising techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
